  • java.lang.Object
    • GameObject
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Background, DisplayBoard, Enemy, Player, Projectile, Tube

    public abstract class GameObject
extends java.lang.Object
    basic Game Object acts as multipurpose container and provides an interface to lowerlevel classes such as the Geometry
